{"id": "1526509569008734279", "channel_id": "1526509569008734279", "author_id": "105610060087996416", "author_name": "ican", "content": "The P-Dive scoring requires you to defeat the whole investigation in as few rounds as possible. The \"unfair\" part is the daily first attempt bonus - some maps have significantly fewer fights and more positive events than others. If you don't get a 2-fight-map, you cannot get the best score at all. The \"unfun\" part is closely tied: Tawil & GMurphy are almost always the core of the team. Tawil can easily play a lot of cards, and even a GMurphy unprimed can deal significant damage through invulnerable. So at the end of the day, your team needs GMurphy, Tawil and a combination of the promoted Chaos & Aequor characters, who don't really get to do much because GMurphy and Tawil are using your resources.  \n\nAs a quick-fix, change the first-attempt-bonus to first-clear-bonus. That way we can take the \"unfair\" part out of the equation and you simply reroll the map until you get a good one.  \n\nIdeally I'd like to see the scoring adjusted like HSR mode: you complete the highest difficulty without Emergency Gnosis, you get the highest reward, no matter how many turns it took. That way, all characters are viable and we can play whatever is fun or we want to try, getting rid of the \"unfun\"\n\nAs a bonus suggestion, allow to select the rule-set to play in (with same rewards between Act1 and Act 2 rules). Especially newer characters are much more fun in Act 2 rules, while Act 1 characters would be more fun in act 1 rules.", "timestamp": "2026-07-14T08:44:02.428000+00:00", "thread_id": "1526509569008734279", "reactions": [{"emoji": "Celeste_agree", "emoji_id": "1400771815076528258", "count": 1}]}
{"id": "1526466457431576576", "channel_id": "1526466457431576576", "author_id": "1509178745121013760", "author_name": "null_06886", "content": "pc端游戏在通关无战斗关卡时游戏会出现卡死的情况，没有最后奖励领取的提示。今天打第五章稳定触发了好几回", "timestamp": "2026-07-14T05:52:43.827000+00:00", "thread_id": "1526466457431576576", "attachments": [{"id": "1526466457670647818", "filename": "6YSJHCHKJ9S50FDCAL.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 775752, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1526466457431576576/1526466457670647818/6YSJHCHKJ9S50FDCAL.png?ex=6a57202b&is=6a55ceab&hm=824fd7fce7e8da736d0ab698636ac97be59597056f4a0b974441e97b5ffcfce5&"}]}
